Class Race

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.com.limaogames.librpg.framework.abstracts.Race
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RaceListener, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Human

    public abstract class Race
extends java.lang.Object
implements RaceListener, java.io.Serializable
    Model class to be inherited by game races classes. Variety of races increments Adventurer personalizations and can be easily created different kinds through this class. Ex: Elfs, Dwarven, Humans, etc.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Limao Games
    Email: andreikeda@limaogames.com.br
    created on: 06/02/2014
    See Also:
    Advantage, Job, RaceListener, Serializable, Serialized Form
